## Step 2: Granting Sudo Access ğŸ›¡ï¸
### Add `devops_user` to sudo group
```bash
sudo usermod -aG sudo devops_user
```
ğŸ“Œ **Explanation:**
- Grants admin privileges to the user.

ğŸ–¼ï¸ **(./images/https://github.com/Yash2526/90DaysOfDevOps/blob/master/2025/linux/Task%20Images/grand%20sudo%20access.png)**
